title: NFL Star Refuses to Participate in Trip to Israel, Reason Why Has Americans Outraged
text:
07:48pm   
Five NFL players from the newly crowned Super Bowl champion New England Patriots have already said they will not visit the White House with their team because of Donald Trump. 
One of those players is Martellus Bennett . 
Bennett’s brother, Michael Bennett of the Seattle Seahawks, has just made a left-leaning political statement of his own. 
Michael has decided to not participate in a scheduled trip to Israel – one of America’s greatest allies – because it is being funded by the Israeli government. 
Seattle Seahawks defensive end Michael Bennett pulled out of a scheduled trip to Israel with 9 other NFL players Friday after he discovered it was being sponsored by the Israeli government. 
Bennett explained the reasons behind his decision in a post on Twitter: 
— Michael Bennett (@mosesbread72) February 11, 2017 
Well, I’m sure the Bennetts have made Obama proud. 
Will the MSM try to use an anti-Semitism angle here? 
No. No, they won’t. LIKE this article?
